data.description: Deltona - IMPROVED PRICE - Welcome Home! This beautiful, move-in ready house offers 3 beds and 2 full baths. It also has an FHA Assumable Loan at 3.99%. It's an open concept floor plan with cathedral ceilings.The kitchen, dining & family room are perfect for entertaining or to supervise playtime or homework. The split bedrooms ensure everyone's privacy. There is ceramic tile in the common areas for easy maintenance and carpet in the bedroom for coziness. You will notice the wonderful Florida light throughout the house. Enjoy your screened-in Florida room year around or a wood fire on the patio! The backyard is fenced and very private. Schedule your showing today!
